extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Store Inventory], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The inventory has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Fruits:] !{data.fruit_count}
      li #[strong Liquids:] !{data.liquid_count}
      li #[strong Solids:] !{data.solid_count}
      li #[strong Spices:] !{data.spice_count}

